data.description: Welcome! This spacious home is peacefully situated on a cul-de-sac, featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 baths with a bonus room in the basement.   The oversized Master stuns with crown molding finishes, barn doors that lead into the master bath and a sun dripped  walk in closet.   The updated Kitchen overlooks the family room, while featuring a breakfast bar, kitchen island, subway tile backsplash and quartz countertops.   The large Family Room boasts vaulted ceilings and a breathtaking brick fireplace. It’s the perfect place to host all your holiday parties!   The Farmers Front Porch, is your go-to zen spot to sip some coffee in your rocking chair. While the Four Season Back Porch, which is connected to the HVAC system, will extend your living space all year round. Plus, a Large Fenced Backyard.   The Partially Finished Basement has an exterior entry and Bonus Room which could be used as a rental space as there is NO HOA.   All 4 bedrooms have ceiling fans and are large enough for king sized beds. Updated fixtures throughout. An entirely cedar upstairs hall closet, which is a really cool feature.   This home is Spacious, Well Maintained & Recently Serviced. Front & side of the home has been Freshly Painted, New Mulch laid, New Back Deck has been completed, Recent Termite Inspection with Transferrable Centricon System, New PVC Plumbing, New Air Purifier installed, Vents were Cleaned/Sanitized 10/25/23 & include a Lifetime Transferrable Warranty, Includes 2 HVACS (only 4/5 years old & recently serviced) and 2 Central Air Units.   Located just a few miles away from Stone Mountain Park! The park offers 15 miles of scenic hiking and walking trails, ranging from easy to moderate. Take it slow and stop to admire the flora and fauna, or let the fresh mountain air invigorate you on a more challenging hike. Locals know this city for its charming village and main street, which include an emerging food scene with plenty of great spots for celebratory meals, causal bites and exciting beverages to sip. Not to mention this home is located close to Schools, Hwy 285 and So Much More! SELLER IS MOTIVATED.
